                     <interp inst="t18291029-247-person1977" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I produce a copy of the conviction of the prisoner by the name of William Passenger (read).</p>
               <p>WILLIAM GALE. I am a timber merchant. I remember the prisoner being tried on that indictment; I attended on the part of my employer - I have no doubt of his being the man.</p>
